comments: Adams (MEM) firms up in Jones' (SAS) path and marginal contact occurs as Adams sets the pick.
Poeltl (SAS) initiates contact with Morant's (MEM) arm during his upward shooting motion, which affects his shot attempt.
Poeltl (SAS) and Morant (MEM) come together and marginal contact occurs as Morant is moving around the pick.
Morant's (MEM) hand brushes Jones' (SAS) arm and marginal contact occurs as Morant defends around the pick.
Adams (MEM) and Poeltl (SAS) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Jones' (SAS) hand slides off of the ball and marginal contact occurs with Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) arm.
Poeltl (SAS) moves alongside Bane's (MEM) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Upon replay review, the contact on this play was deemed a common foul. Richardson (SAS) initiates contact with Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) arm that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Poeltl (SAS) and Jackson Jr. (MEM) come together and marginal contact occurs as both players pursue the loose ball.
After the made basket, Jones (SAS) interferes with the ball and tosses it to the official, preventing it from promptly being put back into play.
Adams (MEM) establishes himself in Jones's (SAS) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Poeltl's (SAS) hand slides off of Morant's (MEM) front and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) jumps vertically and marginal contact occurs while he contests Poeltl's (SAS) shot attempt near the rim.
